# Frontend Structure

## Route component organization

- Route-facing UI components should be defined in dedicated component files, not inline in route definitions.
- Mirror route structure in `src/components/` so component paths reflect route paths.

## Backend/frontend alignment

- Frontend API wrappers in `src/api/` should mirror the backend layout under `src/server/`.
- Components should consume loader-ready data structures that are composed from `src/api/` calls.
